    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a story of <strong>split personality</strong>, where Jack faces a <strong>horrifying</strong> reality: his inner world is no longer under his control. McKinsey, a ruthless and amoral <strong>psychopath</strong>, is tearing his life apart. The only way to get rid of him is through <strong>therapy</strong>. But will that truly solve the problem? McKinsey <strong>threatens</strong> Jack with the loss of everything he holds dear. Can his loved ones survive? And is McKinsey really that dangerous, or is his existence just a part of <strong>something greater</strong>? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/e3435481f75eb6a3134585896e55c6ab.poster.avif?t=1770125439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/e3435481f75eb6a3134585896e55c6ab.webm?t=1770125439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/e3435481f75eb6a3134585896e55c6ab.mp4?t=1770125439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Intriguing narrative with 5 available endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hallucinations that intensify as you progress, distorting reality and affecting the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Handcrafted by a solo developer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Many locations to explore  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your choices do affect the story </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/da84934f430cf0851ef0e18d863109bc.poster.avif?t=1770125439\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/da84934f430cf0851ef0e18d863109bc.webm?t=1770125439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/da84934f430cf0851ef0e18d863109bc.mp4?t=1770125439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this <strong>story-driven adventure game</strong>, players will interact with Jack's world and his visions. Go through <strong>7 days</strong> and set things up so you can get into therapy, without McKinsey understanding. <strong>Interact</strong> with other characters who can help you, <strong>solve puzzles</strong> and act <strong>tricky.</strong> Otherwise McKinsey won't go easy on you...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/0b186c920ce14072fd15f9714b81baff.poster.avif?t=1770125439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/0b186c920ce14072fd15f9714b81baff.webm?t=1770125439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010180/extras/0b186c920ce14072fd15f9714b81baff.mp4?t=1770125439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
